body:
Last game I picked Annie. It was all nice until about 20. minute when fights started. In one particular fight I went in with 3 stacks on stun. Then I used E and immediately R after. Guess what, no one got stunned. It happened 3 times, and it basically lost the match. I just want to know why is that happening. {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} 

This better get fixed soon!

With love, Silver scrub.
